trans-unit.source: Describes the versions of the .NET Framework that an application can run on.
trans-unit.target: 응용 프로그램에서 실행할 수 있는.NET Framework의 버전을 설명 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.CompatibleFramework"></xref> class.
Represents the profile of the corresponding .NET Framework.
A profile is a subset of the full .NET Framework.

For example, the [!INCLUDE[net_client_v35_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v35-long-md.md)] is a subset of the [!INCLUDE[net_v35SP1_long](~/add/includes/net-v35sp1-long-md.md)], and the [!INCLUDE[net_client_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v40-long-md.md)] is a subset of the [!INCLUDE[net_v45](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어는 [!INCLUDE[net_client_v35_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v35-long-md.md)] 의 하위 집합인는 [!INCLUDE[net_v35SP1_long](~/add/includes/net-v35sp1-long-md.md)], 및 [!INCLUDE[net_client_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v40-long-md.md)] 의 하위 집합인는 [!INCLUDE[net_v45](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]합니다.
